549
00:46:51,225 --> 00:46:52,392
Oh.

550
00:46:52,477 --> 00:46:53,852
I drink coffee.

551
00:46:56,189 --> 00:46:57,355
So...

552
00:46:57,440 --> 00:47:00,484
My goodness, this is a surprise.

553
00:47:00,568 --> 00:47:02,986
