Oh, God.

1415
01:47:16,514 --> 01:47:18,181
She was so beautiful.

1416
01:47:18,349 --> 01:47:22,060
- She was wearing this long velvety gown.
- At 8 in the morning?

1417
01:47:22,186 --> 01:47:23,645
Oh, by this time it was 10.

1418
01:47:23,729 --> 01:47:26,106
